# Keep the build context (and image) lean: deps are installed inside the image, and env
# is injected by compose — never bake host node_modules, build output, or secrets in.
node_modules
**/node_modules
dist
**/dist
coverage
**/coverage
playwright-report
**/playwright-report
test-results
**/test-results
.git
.github
docs
.claude
*.log
.env
.env.*
.DS_Store
